OL,3,CAntisemitic hate crime reports to West
OL,4,CMidlands Police more than treble
OL,6,FReports of antisemitic hate crime made
OL,7,Fto West Midlands Police have more than
OL,8,Ftrebled over the past two years,
OL,9,Faccording to a new freedom of
OL,10,Finformation request.
OL,12,FBetween October 2022 and September
OL,13,F2023, the force received 23 reports of
OL,14,Fantisemitic hate crime.
OL,16,FThere were 83 reports of antisemitic
OL,17,Fhate crime between October 2023 and
OL,18,FSeptember 2024 - more than triple that
OL,19,Fof the year before.
