OL,6,FRuth Jacobs, Lay leader of Birmingham
OL,7,F& West Midlands Jewish Community,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We are very aware of the fact
OL,9,Fthat there are demonstrations nearly
OL,10,Fevery week in the West Midlands.
OL,12,F"This has increased the anxiety levels
OL,13,Fin the community who are somewhat
OL,14,Fscared of the intensity of the feeling
OL,16,F"I go to visit other places of worship
OL,17,Fand you knock at the door or it's open
OL,18,Fand you can come in - that's how it
OL,19,Fshould be.
