OL,3,CAntisemitic hate crime reports to West
OL,4,CMidlands Police more than treble
OL,6,FIn October 2023, there were 20 reports
OL,7,Fof antisemitic hate crime - compared
OL,8,Fto 14 reports from January to the end
OL,9,Fof September that year.
OL,11,FWest Midlands Police says it does not
OL,12,Ftolerate any form of discrimination
OL,13,Fand says it has seen an overall
OL,14,Freduction of hate crimes over the last
OL,15,F12 months.
